<% content_for :title, "About — SpaceHub India" %>

<div class="bg-dark text-white py-5 text-center">
  <div class="container py-3">
    <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold mb-3">About SpaceHub India</h1>
    <p class="lead text-secondary col-md-7 mx-auto">We're building India's premier marketplace for unique spaces — making extraordinary venues accessible to creators, professionals, and dreamers.</p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container py-5">
  <div class="row g-5 justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-lg-7">
      <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3">Our Mission</h3>
      <p class="text-muted">Millions of stunning private spaces across India sit empty for most of the day — rooftop terraces, spa suites, recording studios, private dining rooms. Meanwhile, creators, entrepreneurs, and individuals struggle to find inspiring, private spaces to work, create, and celebrate.</p>
      <p class="text-muted">SpaceHub connects the two. By making it easy to list, discover, and book unique spaces by the hour, we're creating new income streams for space owners while giving guests access to experiences that were once out of reach.</p>

      <h3 class="fw-bold mb-3 mt-5">Technology</h3>
      <p class="text-muted">SpaceHub is built on Rails 8 with a modern Hotwire frontend. We use Claude AI to help hosts write compelling listing descriptions. Payments are powered by Razorpay (for domestic UPI and card transactions) and Stripe (for international cards).</p>

      <div class="row g-3 mt-2">
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
          <div class="card border-0 bg-light py-3">
            <div class="h4 fw-bold text-warning mb-0">6</div>
            <div class="text-muted small">Cities</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
          <div class="card border-0 bg-light py-3">
            <div class="h4 fw-bold text-warning mb-0">3</div>
            <div class="text-muted small">Categories</div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 text-center">
          <div class="card border-0 bg-light py-3">
            <div class="h4 fw-bold text-warning mb-0">2</div>
            <div class="text-muted small">Payment Gateways</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
